Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: President Bush and the 1990 national budget
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yg2bp
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 19 Oct 1990
President Bush and the Senate struggling to agree on a national budget, the workings of the federal system, and the 1990 Congressional elections, as detailed by Alistair Cooke.